# Debug-output artifacts (generated by debug test suites)
# Ignore everything under debug-output/ by default — these files are
# regenerated by `npx vitest run src/__tests__/debug/...`. EXCEPTIONS :
# we DO push the rman/ and oracle/ transcripts so they can be reviewed
# on GitHub without running the suites locally.
debug-output/*
!debug-output/rman/
!debug-output/oracle/
!debug-output/linux/
